/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-012 任务清单\n  Line 4: > **AR**: AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n  Line 107: - [ ] T-007.01 补全 `changes/AR-012/design.md` 第 1 节：架构定位（Store 作为 K8s 状态缓存层，为 Router/GC/Reconciler 提供会话存储）\n  Line 146: | `changes/AR-012/design.md` | 修改 | 补全所有 TODO 章节 |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-012/proposal.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n  Line 9: - **AR**: AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-012/design.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-012: 会话存储接口定义 — 设计说明\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/design.md:\n  Line 612: | AR-012 | 基于 Prometheus 的动态负载均衡 | P2 |","metadata":{"matches":20,"truncated":false},"title":"AR-012","time":{"start":1775851109849,"end":1775851109871}}}}
