{"type":"text","timestamp":1775851133044,"sessionID":"ses_28706999cffeGRH9hcQ8s0loip","part":{"id":"prt_d78f9ceee001jm9bueSqqrVG92","messageID":"msg_d78f9c063001JuEkN83UXHYJRG","sessionID":"ses_28706999cffeGRH9hcQ8s0loip","type":"text","text":"## AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Summary\n\n**Completed:**\n- Phase 1 (Core Interface & Errors): `pkg/store/store.go`, `pkg/store/errors.go`\n- Phase 2 (Implementation): `pkg/store/singleton.go`, `pkg/store/store_redis.go`, `pkg/store/store_valkey.go`\n\n**Deferred:**\n- Phase 3 (Unit Tests): All test files pending — `store_redis_test.go`, `store_valkey_test.go`, `singleton_test.go` not created\n\nThe implementation compiles and satisfies the core delta-spec requirements (interface contract, provider selection, environment config, session CRUD, atomicity, index maintenance). Unit tests remain as the remaining work.","time":{"start":1775851133043,"end":1775851133043}}}
